@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="home-container">
    <section class="main-section">
        <div class="main-section-text">
            <h1>Plan and Visualize Your Instagram Feed</h1>
            <p>Organize your posts before publishing to maintain a consistent and professional feed.</p>
            <p>
                <b>Instagram Feed Planner</b> allows you to arrange posts, preview your grid, and plan your feed into the future.
            </p>
            <div>
                <a href="planner" class="startButton">
                    <span>Start Planning Now</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="preview-video">
            <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
                <source src="videos/preview.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                Your browser does not support this video.
            </video>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section">
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Arrange and Preview Posts</h2>
            <p>Easily move, reorder, and preview posts to plan your feed exactly how you want before publishing on your social media.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Multiple Feed Planning</h2>
            <p>Manage multiple feeds in parallel, keeping all your separate accounts organized and consistent.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Fast, Local, and Private</h2>
            <p>The planner runs entirely in your browser. All data is stored locally, ensuring privacy and fast performance.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="donation-section">
        <div class="donation-text">
            <h3>Support the Project</h3>
            <p>
                Instagram Feed Planner is a free tool designed to help users plan efficiently. If you find it useful, consider making a donation to support this project and my other free tools.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>